  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The research objectives are to test the efficacy of a Modified CIMT treatment in babies
      diagnosed with hemiplegia, treated in a home program, as compared to a control group of
      babies receiving a parallel home program but with no CIMT.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
